cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.DL 

This paper discusses the use of deep learning for recommendation systems in marketplaces, which involves natural language processing (text), image analysis, and user behavior data. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IR (Information Retrieval), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.DL (Deep Learning).
